        "title": "",
        "subhead": "it all starts on pasture",
        "text": "<p>You can't get leather without ruminants. Sorry to break it to ya bud, it's just one of those things.<\/p><p>Healthy goats that live on pasture year round make the rugged hides that we prize for their leather's durability and longevity.<\/p>",
