    "51b8bedb-7336-4a15-9d51-568840189976": {
      "type": "text",
      "settings": {
        "headline": "",
        "subhead": "STRETCH GLOVESTRONG",
        "text": "<p>It takes a tremendous understanding of hide dynamics to cut out all 24 pieces that make up our flagship Vermonter glove. Every section of a hide stretches in a particular way, and we make sure that each piece we cut stretches in the way we want it to, taking advantage of the natural properties of the leather.<\/p>",
        "link_text": "Read More",
        "link": "",
        "bg_color": "#ffffff",
        "text_color": "#452c80"
      }
    },
    "1d3a052d-d49d-40f1-9444-2ef32c61ab4a": {
      "type": "history",
      "settings": {
        "title": "",
        "subhead": "DID WE MENTION OUR COMMITMENT TO QUALITY?",
        "text": "<p>After all the pieces are cut, they come upstairs to Heidi's desk. Fourth generation glove maker, Heidi Haupt uses her eagle eyes to ensure every single piece is unblemished and fit to become a glove.<\/p>",
        "media_type": "uploaded_video",
        "upload_video_url": "https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/videos\/c\/o\/v\/d246188ef7a94518a0e2b830e07d00aa.mp4",
