    "08b45b19-3417-4781-8e31-74c24478e6c3": {
      "type": "history",
      "settings": {
        "title": "",
        "subhead": "A GLOVE BEYOND COMPARE",
        "text": "<p>Leather is a natural material. There are subtle variations in the color, tone and overall appearance from hide to hide. Since we pay an extreme amount of attention to detail through our entire process, our last step is to match a left and right glove by eye. <\/p>",
